:

1. *Govorili* smo o njoj pre nekoliko nedelja. (We talked about her a few weeks ago.)
2. Oni su *govorili* o njoj još pre nekoliko meseci. (They talked about her a few months ago.)
3. Ona je *govorila* da će doći. (She said she was coming.)
4. On je rekao da su oni *govorili* o tome. (He said they were talking about it.)
5. Ona me je pitala šta smo *govorili*. (She asked me what we were talking about.)
6. Neki od njih su *govorili* o tome. (Some of them were talking about it.)